a syndicated
columnist and also with the
"NewsHour," David

27:41.527 --> 27:49.434 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Brooks, columnist with The New
York Times,
Amy Walter of The Cook Political
Report.

27:49.535 --> 27:55.340 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
To all three of you, we're
waiting for Donald
Trump to be nominated, but today
has been

27:55.440 --> 28:00.245 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
